H0.text: What breed of dog is the ‘Monopoly’ playing piece, or token. Poodle

H1.text: What breed of dog is the ‘Monopoly’ playing piece, or token. Beagle

H2.text: What breed of dog is the ‘Monopoly’ playing piece, or token. Dachshund

H3.text: What breed of dog is the ‘Monopoly’ playing piece, or token. Scottie

A4.text: The eight playable tokens at the time included the Battleship, Boot, Cat, Racecar, Scottie Dog, Thimble, Top hat, and Wheelbarrow.
